model.towers

Class Tower

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Entity
      • model.towers.Tower
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AreaTower, CheapTower, ExpensiveTower, MultiShotTower, OneShotTower, PiercingTower, RapidTower

    public class Tower
extends Entity
    A minimal template for the different Towers that can be drawn and used in the game.
    Author:
    Ethan Glasberg (glasberg@email.arizona.edu), Jarod Bristol (jarodkylebristol@email.arizona.edu), Alex Gonzalez (aegonzalez793@email.arizona.edu), Patrick Dearborn (pdearborn@email.arizona.edu)
